column2: If a country *is in Europe*, what is the chance (or probability) that it won at least one gold medal in the last Olympics? Give your best guess (between 0 and 1).
If a country *is outside of Europe*, what is the chance (or probability) that it won at least one gold medal in the last Olympics? Give your best guess (between 0 and 1).
What is the chance (or probability) of a country *being located in Europe*?
If people in a country *use less energy per person than *, what is the chance (or probability) that it won at least one gold medal in the last Olympics? Give your best guess (between 0 and 1).
Among 10 countries *whose electricity consumption is less than 63.2 billion kWh*, how many won one or more medals in the last Olympics?
Among 10 countries, how many have an *electricity consumption of more than 63.2 billion kWh*?
If a country *is in Middle East & North Africa region*, what is the chance (or probability) that it won at least one gold medal in the last Olympics? Give your best guess (between 0 and 1).
If a country *outside of Middle East & North Africa region*, what is the chance (or probability) that it won at least one gold medal in the last Olympics? Give your best guess (between 0 and 1).
What is the chance (or probability) of a country *being located in Middle East & North Africa region*?
Among 10 countries *whose military expenditures are more than 3.1% of GDP*, how many won one or more medals in the last Olympics?
